$pi = 2.0*acos(0.0);

TEXT(beginproblem()); 



##SHORTCUT COMMANDS
$ds = "\displaystyle";
$d = "\hbox{d}";

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));
The average value of \(\sin x\) in the interval \([0,\pi]\) is
 \{ans_rule(30)\}.
EOT
ANS(num_cmp("2/pi"));


SOLUTION(EV3(<<'EOT')); 
$BR $BBOLD Solution:$EBOLD The average value is
\[\bar f = \frac{\int_0^\pi \sin x}{\pi - 0} = \frac{2}{\pi}.\]


EOT





